{"tid":1198520,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"想11號晚/12號幫手嘅入一入黎","createTime":"2019-06-10T09:06:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T09:38:35.000Z","uid":201266,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"756dc51d5120bac319ae31ef131183c3e18e573a","tid":1198520,"uid":201266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:06:00.000Z","msg":"發夢到時會用以下物資<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n物資表：<br />\n重要：大聲公，對講機<br />\n<br />\n食水, 眼罩, 口罩, 乾糧餅乾，頭盔，長遮，短遮，雨衣，寶礦力同candy bar, baking soda, 防割/工業手套，防曬手袖，泳鏡，護目鏡，膠手套，工頭鞋，保鮮紙，毛巾<br />\n<br />\n急救組 需要既物資<br />\n1. distilled water / 生理鹽水<br />\n2. 紗布 重要<br />\n3. 冰袋/ 小林退熱貼 重要<br />\n4. 醫生膠布<br />\n5. 手套<br />\n6. 崩帶 重要<br />\n7. 三角巾 重要<br />\n8. 膠布 重要<br />\n9. 廚房紙<br />\n10. 對講機<br />\n11. 保鮮紙 重要<br />\n12. 索帶<br />\n13.護目鏡 重要<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n大家記住唔好大懵唔覺意擺低呢啲嘢係垃圾會出面啦 <br />\n唔係比人偷左黎用就唔係咁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d36de198c0a4ef2b53f1a7b5619df47e421448bd","tid":1198520,"uid":201266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:06:16.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"0f89f3db1973317259386437c576f1842487dd29","tid":1198520,"uid":201266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:06:28.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"faf45edf3f42050b1431b8a305676f89c745cbaa","tid":1198520,"uid":217844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:38:35.000Z","msg":"推"}]}